myself, oh, my god.

00:01:41.060 --> 00:01:43.410 align:middle line:90%
I forgot to get married.

00:01:43.410 --> 00:01:46.730 align:middle line:84%
And I started thinking about,
how did I get to be 43,

00:01:46.730 --> 00:01:47.990 align:middle line:90%
never married?

00:01:47.990 --> 00:01:49.340 align:middle line:90%
I had this great life.

00:01:49.340 --> 00:01:50.660 align:middle line:90%
Everything was good.

00:01:50.660 --> 00:01:54.260 align:middle line:84%
